channel.title: CVE Feed for Jenkins Project -- Jenkins MATLAB Plugin
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins Project -- Jenkins MATLAB Plugin

item.title: CVE-2023-49656|2024-08-02T22:01:26.016Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20matlab%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins MATLAB Plugin 2.11.0 and earlier does not configure its XML parser to prevent XML external entity (XXE) attacks.

item.title: CVE-2023-49654|2024-08-02T22:01:25.660Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20matlab%20plugin
item.description: Missing permission checks in Jenkins MATLAB Plugin 2.11.0 and earlier allow attackers to have Jenkins parse an XML file from the Jenkins controller file system.

item.title: CVE-2023-49655|2024-08-02T22:01:25.849Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20matlab%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in Jenkins MATLAB Plugin 2.11.0 and earlier allows attackers to have Jenkins parse an XML file from the Jenkins controller file system.
